msgid ""
"Fill out the template details above (optional - Excel file may contain the "
"name), then import an Excel file to populate the template structure. The "
"template will be created with the information you provide, and the Excel "
"file will add sections, pages, and items. If the Excel file contains a "
"template name, it will be used."
